snippet.title: Pokemon Channel Gameplay
snippet.description:
Pokemon Channel for the Gamecube, was captured from the Gamecube console and game disc. Some reviews have said that Pokemon Channel "isn't really a game," but I find it to be interactive and to be able to connect with the Pokemon world.

Publisher: Nintendo
Developer: Ambrella
Released on: December 1, 2003 (North America)
Platform: GameCube

Pokemon Channel wiki:
https://pokemon.fandom.com/wiki/Pok%C3%A9mon_Channel
Pokemon Channel Gamecube trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MgdtrVA3Scg
